---
title: Triple Cheese Spinach Penne Bake 2x the delicious servings!
description: Who doesn’t daydream about cheesy baked pasta? Luckily, this big batch crowd-pleaser will make those dreams come true for the whole crew. In it, you’ll find penne and spinach in a rich marinara sauce layered with melty mozzarella and our savory Italian cheese blend. In the oven, the ingredients bubble together and the flavors meld into savory dinner perfection. You’ll whisk it to the table—with toppings of buttery toasted panko, Parmesan, and chili flakes—and serve it straight from the dish for maximum cheese pull and rounds of oohs and aahs!
